  "texts": [
    "Relying solely on LLM-generated opinions without appropriate fine-tuning is irresponsible.",
    "Even with fine-tuning, LLMs may produce unpredictable responses.",
    "We advocate for a responsible approach that integrates LLMs with DS-Models, where DS-Models guide LLM responses, positioning LLMs primarily as intermediaries between users and DS-Models.",
    "Although this approach limits LLM flexibility, it enhances security and control.",
    "Nonetheless, even with DS-Model guidance, inaccuracies can still occur."
  ],
